'''解码宇宙：新信息科学看天地万物'''（{{lang-en|''Decoding the Universe: How the New Science of Information Is Explaining Everything in the Cosmos, from Our Brains to Black Holes''}}）是美国作家[[查尔斯·塞费|查尔斯·塞费]]2007年出版的一本关于[[信息论|信息论]]的书籍，是他的第三部科普作品<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B000O76NFK|publisher=[[amazon.com|amazon.com]]|title =Decoding the Universe: How the New Science of Information Is Explaining Everything in the Cosmos, from Our Brains to Black Holes by Charles Seife|accessdate=2015-07-23}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Decoding+the+universe%3B+how+the+new+science+of+information+is...-a0164405845|publisher=[[thefreelibrary.com|thefreelibrary.com]]|title=Decoding the Universe by Charles Seife|accessdate=2015-07-23|archive-date=2017-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109193956/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Decoding+the+universe%3b+how+the+new+science+of+information+is...-a0164405845|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://rhapsodyinbooks.wordpress.com/2009/04/27/review-of-decoding-the-universe-by-charles-seife/|publisher=rhapsodyinbooks.wordpress.com|title=Review of "Decoding the Universe" by Charles Seife|date=April 27, 2009|first=|last=|access-date=2020-08-07|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304185559/https://rhapsodyinbooks.wordpress.com/2009/04/27/review-of-decoding-the-universe-by-charles-seife/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==梗概==
本书围绕[[信息论|信息论]]展开，讨论了其中的许多问题，如[[退相干|退相干]]与概率、[[相对论|相对论]]与[[量子力学|量子力学]]，特别是[[艾伦·图灵|艾伦·图灵]]和[[埃尔温·薛定谔|埃尔温·薛定谔]]的工作。
